{"tid":1119481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實賓斯馬根本球王級","createTime":"2019-04-22T03:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:04:44.000Z","uid":213217,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2e7d6d7096e526854444544b341336835a40ea","tid":1119481,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"賓斯馬咁勁，先30歲仲當打，今年一定可以50球收尾。 歐聯如果唔係場地太硬應該可以場場入幾球幫隊波晉級，過幾年歐聯決賽周入球就可以刷新60球記錄。<br />\n<br />\n前2季必入球9成炒，人人都反個時只係賓賓唔認真同比人騎，我相信賓賓解放後一定可以搶金球，破歐聯入球記錄，創隊史入波記錄<br />\n<br />\n吾賓萬歲萬萬歲。"},{"pid":"7a5aa424f09680c41e5b45018749766c990d9f8f","tid":1119481,"uid":217108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"係美斯應該去跟佢學下踢波"},{"pid":"2045b60ac33b6c097aa2c6268df4faabed6e6a42","tid":1119481,"uid":170772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"認同 C朗都好意思自稱球王<br />\n點解佢唔得？"},{"pid":"eb226ea7112de81d1aae504afd650f3dda2fe8cd","tid":1119481,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2045b60ac33b6c097aa2c6268df4faabed6e6a42","tid":1119481,"uid":170772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"認同 C朗都好意思自稱球王<br />\n點解佢唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}